name: HKBloodType
desc: Constants indicating the user’s blood type.

items.name: case notSet
items.desc: Either the user’s blood type is not set, or the user has not granted your app permission to read the blood type.

items.name: case aPositive
items.desc: The user has an A+ blood type.

items.name: case aNegative
items.desc: The user has an A– blood type.

items.name: case bPositive
items.desc: The user has an B+ blood type.

items.name: case bNegative
items.desc: The user has an B– blood type.

items.name: case abPositive
items.desc: The user has an AB+ blood type.

items.name: case abNegative
items.desc: The user has an AB– blood type.

items.name: case oPositive
items.desc: The user has an O+ blood type.

items.name: case oNegative
items.desc: The user has an O– blood type.
